# =============================================================================
# File: .env.secret.example
# Path: .env.secret   (copy this template to `.env.secret`, then fill values)
# Description: TEMPLATE for the Tier-2 secret env file of the LOCAL
#              docker-compose dev stack (loaded LAST by `e2e_stack.sh dev`,
#              `required: false`). Copy to `.env.secret` (git-ignored, NEVER
#              committed) and fill REAL values. CLAUDE.md §4.6.
#
#              Only the genuinely-secret C8 credentials live here ; the rest
#              of the dev stack's config (Arango / MinIO / per-component)
#              comes from `ay_platform_core/tests/.env.test` defaults.
# =============================================================================

# Shared C8 gateway credential — presented by C3/C4/sub-agents as the Bearer
# AND enforced by the LiteLLM proxy as its master_key. Pick any strong
# shared secret (e.g. `sk-aywizz-proxy-<random>`).
C8_GATEWAY_API_KEY=

# Real Anthropic provider key — read ONLY by the LiteLLM proxy (never by a
# client component). Format: `sk-ant-...`.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
